### <a id="mysql"></a> Configure MySQL Settings

<%= vars.product_short %> can either use the Tanzu SQL for VMs service or an external MySQL database.
To use the Tanzu SQL for VMs service, you must have the tile installed.

Follow the steps below to configure MySQL settings.

#### Use the Tanzu SQL for VMs Service


If you have Tanzu SQL for VMs installed and want to use the service:

1. Click **MySQL Settings**.

1. Select **MySQL Service**.
1. Enter the Tanzu SQL for VMs service plan you want to use.
The service plan you enter must be a single node plan. For example, `db-small`.
  ![MySQL Settings Service Option](images/mysql-settings-service.png)<%# Images require alt text that describes the image in detail. %>

1. Click **Save**.

